          </p>
        </statement>
        <solution>
          <p>
            Using software, we would obtain a tail area of 0.4038. If using the table in Appendix<nbsp/>C, we would have identified that the tail area is larger than 0.3 but not be able to give the precise value.
          </p>
        </solution>
